---

<section class="root">
  <SectionTitle title="お知らせ" subtitle="NEWS" />

  <div class="post-area">
    <article class="post">
      <a href="news.html#20250522" class="post-link">
        <p class="post-link-date">2025/05/22</p>
        <h3>【Jr.】2025年度の団員募集チラシを更新しました</h3>
